MiningRigRentals.Title: %algorithmex% mining with RainbowMiner rig %rigid%
MiningRigRentals.Description: Autostart mining with RainbowMiner (https://rbminer.net) on Linux. This rig is idle and will activate itself, as soon, as you rent it. %workername%
MiningRigRentals.StartMessage: Dear renter, thank you for renting my rig. It will be up-and-running in no time: offline pool or zero hashrate is normal in the first 5-10 minutes. Please allow at least 10 minutes to pass before raising an issue. Happy mining! (Automated message, do not respond)
MiningRigRentals.ExtensionMessage: Dear renter, your rental will end soon. Now would be a good time to extend the rental, if you are happy with the result.
MiningRigRentals.PoolOfflineMessage: Dear renter, it looks like your pool is currently offline. Please check your settings.
